{
  "stem": "1169.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were people who, at night, were like professional storytellers who would get up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And most stories that people said were like hindsight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were a lot of people with us who just came back from Western Europe to Hungary, because they didn't think this would happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People told us all types of stories how if they would have known, they wouldn't have to be here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I remember one announcement, which I'll never forget, because that really says it all, how it was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had the richest Hungarian Jew in our midst.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was like the President of the Hungarian community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "His name was Freudiger, an older gentlemen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Somehow, he smuggled a can of sardines into Bergen-Belsen, and he opened it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He turned around for one second, and it was gone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That night, he makes an announcement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And as you know, this was the symbol, this Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Freudiger, the symbol of aristocracy, of civility, of dignity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, who stole my can of sardines?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm asking it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm asking him to give it back to me, because I've spit into it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When people heard that, they said, God, we really are in the gutter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If a man like Freudiger can make such a statement, then we are in the gutter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That really depressed everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, like, said it all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It reflected our true state of being.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are in the gutter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As a kid, we did not do slave labor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People had time, all day gossip and talking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I listened in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had very big ears, and I listened to everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I took a lot of stuff to heart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was a tremendous amount of self-blame.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
